data.description:
A clean and feature-rich analog watchface. Now supports Pebble Time.

Date and time:
- day of week;
- day of month;
- seconds hand (configurable).

Weather:
- temperature in °C and °F (configurable);
- weather condition;
- location detected automatically;
- never stale, updated hourly.

Battery:
- percentage;
- charging state;
- only shown when charge is low or Pebble is plugged.

Bluetooth:
- connection status;
- vibrate on disconnect (configurable).
